# What I made

Something like the Claude app, entirely vibe-coded but over a week with painstakingly detailed prompting. It can search the web, use tools, code artifacts, expand it's own functionality and floats on my Mac screen in the corner.

Repo: [https://github.com/tarunmugunthan/pill-ai](https://github.com/tarunmugunthan/pill-ai)

